<section class="comparison panel panel--glass" aria-labelledby="comparison-heading">
  <div class="comparison__header">
    <p class="eyebrow">Where to start</p>
    <h3 id="comparison-heading">Institute or Studio?</h3>
    <p class="muted">
      Institute = open guides and diagnostics you can run yourself. Studio = facilitated engagements when you
      need a delivery partner.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid--two comparison__grid">
    <article class="card comparison__card">
      <div class="card__glow" aria-hidden="true" />
      <p class="eyebrow">Institute</p>
      <h4>Open guidance and self-serve diagnostics.</h4>
      <p>Use the free library to align teams and run diagnostics when you want a quick readiness pulse.</p>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="button primary" href="/library">
          Browse the library
        </a>
        <a class="button ghost" href="/diagnostics">
          Run a diagnostic
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>
    <article class="card comparison__card">
      <div class="card__glow" aria-hidden="true" />
      <p class="eyebrow">Studio</p>
      <h4>Facilitated engagements when you need a partner.</h4>
      <p>Bring in the Studio for bespoke facilitation, governance escalations, or embedded delivery support.</p>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="button primary" href="https://ethotechnics.com/studio" rel="noreferrer">
          Visit the Studio
        </a>
        <a class="button ghost" href="mailto:studio@ethotechnics.org">
          Email the Studio team
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
